cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DL 

This paper discusses the use of parametric models in reinforcement learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), control systems (cs.SY), and deep learning (cs.DL). The paper specifically focuses on the comparison between parametric models and experience replay, which is a common technique used in reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.AI, followed by cs.RO and cs.SY, and finally cs.DL.
